        <title>德國博班申請全紀錄：如何準備到拿到Offer</title>
        <author>
            <name>Chueh 珏</name>
        </author>
        <link href="https://chueh1115blog.github.io/de-guo-bo-ban-shen-qing-quan-ji-luru-he-zhun-bei-dao-na-dao-offer.html"/>
        <id>https://chueh1115blog.github.io/de-guo-bo-ban-shen-qing-quan-ji-luru-he-zhun-bei-dao-na-dao-offer.html</id>
